LOGIC NODES — AUTOMATION & CONTROL FLOW
SPLIT TEXT + LIST SELECTOR (PAIR)
Use case: Process multiple items from a single text input. 
CODE  233CHARS
CODE  54CHARS
Or to pick one specific item: 
PROMPT CONCATENATOR
CODE  73CHARS
Use case: Join multiple text inputs before a generation node when no LLM processing is needed. 
Faster than Text Assistant, no credits consumed Use only when you want a mechanical join, not intelligent processing 
HUMAN REVIEW
Use case: Any production pipeline where quality matters before output is published. 
CODE  49CHARS
INSERT_AFTER_ANY_GENERATION_NODE_THAT_PRODUCES_CONTENT_FOR_REVIEW The workflow pauses, a human approves or rejects the asset, then execution continues.
ROUTER
CODE  201CHARS
Use case: Send one node's output to multiple downstream nodes without duplicating or re-running. The image is generated once; Router distributes it to all four paths. 
RENAME ASSET
CODE  79CHARS
Use case: Organized file naming, especially before Google Drive export. 
